OL,3,CThousands in North London without gas
OL,4,Cafter water floods pipes in Muswell
OL,5,CHill
OL,7,FClick above to watch Kaf Okpattah's
OL,8,Freport.
OL,10,FThousands of homes and businesses in
OL,11,Fnorth London are without gas after
OL,12,Fwater flooded the pipes.
OL,14,FAround 3,000 people have been affected
OL,15,Fafter a burst water main flooded the
OL,16,Fgas network in Muswell Hill on Sunday.
OL,17,FThe disruption has also impacted
OL,18,FColney Hatch and Hornsey.
