OL,3,CThousands in North London without gas
OL,4,Cafter water floods pipes in Muswell
OL,5,CHill
OL,7,FCadent, which manages the UK's
OL,8,FNational Gas Emergency Service, said
OL,9,Fit is in the "early stages" of
OL,10,Fresolving the issue and has urged
OL,11,Fresidents and business owners to be
OL,12,Fpatient while work continues.
OL,14,FOne of the residents affected is
OL,15,FMatthew Robinson, who has been left
OL,16,Fwithout heating in his home. He has
OL,17,Fhad to travel to his mother's house to
OL,18,Fhave hot showers.
