OL,5,CHill
OL,7,FHe told ITV News: "In the morning, we
OL,8,Fwent to bed and everything seemed
OL,9,Ffine, but that's when we'd heard that
OL,10,Fit would take three days to fix. So,
OL,11,FI'm sort of making alternative plans.
OL,12,FAnd then in the morning, the gas was
OL,13,Foff completely. The water's on, but
OL,14,Fit's just cold."
OL,16,FLocal businesses are also feeling the
OL,17,Fstrain. Among them is Lal Hardy, who
OL,18,Fruns a tattoo shop in Muswell Hill.
