OL,5,CHill
OL,7,FHe said: "If there's no heating, it's
OL,8,Fdefinitely going to affect our
OL,9,Fbusiness because people have to get in
OL,10,Fa state of some undress to be tattooed
OL,11,Fand they'll be sat here for a while.
OL,13,F"We have got an industrial heater
OL,14,Fwhich hopefully will be all right, but
OL,15,Fif it's not, we'll have to cancel
OL,16,Feveryone.
