OL,7,F"Which means that, you know, in a time
OL,8,Fof economic, really downturn, every
OL,9,Fcustomer we lose or have to postpone,
OL,10,Fyou know, it's costing us and it's not
OL,11,Fthe ideal thing for us, really."
OL,13,FCadent's Network Director and incident
OL,14,Fcontroller, Vicky Grieve, said it is
OL,15,Ftoo early to provide a timeline for
OL,16,Frepairs.
