OL,5,CHill
OL,7,FShe told ITV News: "Obviously, with
OL,8,Feverything that it takes to resolve
OL,9,Fit, we have to first take all the
OL,10,Fwater out the gas main. We're working
OL,11,Fas quickly and as safely as possible,
OL,12,Fbut with situations like this, it's
OL,13,Freally difficult based on the fact
OL,14,Fthat it's a long process."
OL,16,FA customer support team has been set
OL,17,Fup at Freehold Community Centre, where
OL,18,Fresidents have been queuing to collect
OL,19,Fheaters and blankets.
